    m_Alignment: 1
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: '







    _




    Our aspirational goal is to send our first cargo mission to Mars in 2022. The
    objectives for the first mission will be to confirm water resources and identify
    hazards along with putting in place initial power, mining, and life support infrastructure.





    A Second mission, with both cargo and crew, is targeted for 2024, with primary
    objectives of building a propellant depot and preparing for future crew flights.
    The ships from these initial missions will also serve as the beginnings of our
    first Mars base, from which we can build a thriving city and eventually a self-sustaining
    civilzation on Mars.

    -'
